T - 355 days    religion must look like a waste of time

[[
So, the novel makes religion "look like a waste of time"
in that it presents religion as very time consuming,
but in a hopefully positive light.

Some atheists will read this chapter as confirmation of
its subtitle, that spending this much effort chasing
after something that does not exist is truly a waste
